<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好了！” 厨师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我弄丢了食谱！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今晚就是国王的宴会了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33399</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有食谱，我就做不出食物！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来帮你！” 汤姆说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挥动了魔杖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43162</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“出现吧，食谱！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆听到 “轰” 的一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是食谱没有出现。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克生气地走进厨房。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“王后在图书馆看书。” 德克厉声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“书架突然爆炸了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是你干的吗，汤姆?”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“糟了。” 汤姆说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78040</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们在找食谱。” 厨师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就快找！” 德克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“客人们快要到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>宴会一定要完美！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快帮我找找吧，汤姆！” 厨师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在整个城堡里找。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在架子和桌子底下找。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在储存室和花园里找。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们还是找不到食谱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，他们回到了厨房。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>厨师很担心。“太糟糕了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137746</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有个主意！” 汤姆说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137746</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要做一种魔法粉末。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144472</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它可以让你做的食物变得好吃！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那太好了，汤姆。” 厨师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有食谱，我就做不出食物！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克把头伸进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的咒语一定要成功，魔法师！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>要不然你们俩都得进恐怖地牢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>